arts.ttl: Elche star ruled out of Real Oviedo clash
arts.sum: A member of the attacking ranks at Elche has been ruled out of the club’s upcoming meeting with fellow La Liga newcomers Real Oviedo. The player in question? Álvaro Rodríguez.…
